organic.title: Texas Oncology-Presbyterian Cancer Center Dallas
organic.snippet: Driving Directions. We're located on the campus of Texas Health Presbyterian Dallas. Travel south on Greenville Avenue, past Walnut Hill Lane. Turn right (west) onto Phoenix Drive and then right (north) on Fogelson Lane. Follow the signs to the cancer center. Download map · Full Driving Directions · New Patient Forms.
